      "beast_baseline": "wait sorry, what? i just need the actual logistics info. can you just stick to the technical side of the risk transfer? i'm trying to figure out if we need to take out our own additional coverage if we use CIF or if the seller's policy is enough to cover us for theft or damage during the voyage.",
